---
import Container from '../ui/Container.astro';
---

<section id="proc-nase-weby" class="py-20 md:py-28 bg-neutral-50 scroll-mt-20">
  <Container>
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      <!-- Nadpis -->
      <div class="text-center mb-14 md:mb-18">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-neutral-800 mb-4 leading-tight">
          Proč naše weby <span class="relative inline-block px-3 py-1"><span class="absolute inset-0 bg-[#fdc700] rounded-sm -z-10" aria-hidden="true"></span><span class="relative z-10 text-neutral-800">vydělávají víc</span></span> než běžná konkurence
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-neutral-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Za 10+ let jsme viděli, co funguje a co ne. Naše struktury a obsah vychází z reálných dat — ne z pocitu, jak by web měl vypadat.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- 3 karty -->
      <div class="mb-14 md:mb-18">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
          <div class="group bg-neutral-50 rounded-2xl p-6 border-2 border-transparent hover:border-[#fdc700] transition-all">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[#292e4c] rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4 text-white">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 21l-6-6m2-5a7 7 0 11-14 0 7 7 0 0114 0z" /><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z" /></svg>
            </div>
            <p class="font-semibold text-neutral-800 mb-2">Analýzy tisíců vyhledávacích dotazů</p>
            <p class="text-neutral-600 text-sm">Ahrefs, Google Search data</p>
          </div>
          <div class="group bg-neutral-50 rounded-2xl p-6 border-2 border-transparent hover:border-[#fdc700] transition-all">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[#292e4c] rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4 text-white">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z" /></svg>
            </div>
            <p class="font-semibold text-neutral-800 mb-2">Reálných konverzních dat</p>
            <p class="text-neutral-600 text-sm">Z oborů služeb a B2B</p>
          </div>
          <div class="group bg-neutral-50 rounded-2xl p-6 border-2 border-transparent hover:border-[#fdc700] transition-all">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[#292e4c] rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4 text-white">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 5a1 1 0 011-1h14a1 1 0 011 1v2a1 1 0 01-1 1H5a1 1 0 01-1-1V5zM4 13a1 1 0 011-1h6a1 1 0 011 1v6a1 1 0 01-1 1H5a1 1 0 01-1-1v-6zM16 13a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v6a1 1 0 01-1 1h-2a1 1 0 01-1-1v-6z" /></svg>
            </div>
            <p class="font-semibold text-neutral-800 mb-2">Ověřených SEO struktur</p>
            <p class="text-neutral-600 text-sm">Které Google dlouhodobě preferuje</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Každý web je postavený tak, aby: -->
      <div class="mb-14 md:mb-18 text-center">
        <p class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-800 mb-6">Každý web je postavený na datech, ne na pocitu.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Závěrečný punch -->
      <div class="text-center py-10 md:py-14 px-6 bg-neutral-800 rounded-2xl">
        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-neutral-400 mb-2">Ne hezký web.</p>
        <p class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-[#fdc700]">Funkční web.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Container>
</section>
